        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": ": \"Follow the water down. Follow the heaviest stream.\"",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "bold"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " - The party said their goodbyes and set out down the underground river toward the source of everything."
